My  name is Naaisha Riley This Morning at 2:30 am I went to the Dunkin Donuts located at 601 East Fordham Road in the Bronx, Store number 349896, where I was told that they are  closed  for business by a young black female on the overnight shift, I asked her so There's no way that i Can have coffee at this time, she stated no. I said that's  odd because i always come here around this time every day to get a cup of coffee.  I asked and why is this location closed for business, she stated that her boss and the owner told her to close the store for business when i asked the young lady her name she asked  me why. I want this  company to know that as a company or a Franchise you are false advertising by claiming to be 24 hours on line and from  the ad posting out side the store. I just wanted the owner to know that you just lost 3  customers today. very unprofessional and rude workers.. I will be making a formal complaint to corporate.
